</div></div><div class="bg-blur-layer"></div><div class="bg-animated-image-container absolute"><div class="lazy-image-blur bg-animated-image" style="background-size:contain;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position:center"><img loading="lazy" src="https://minio.nanosemantics.ru/prod-nanosemanticsru-site-media/macbkt_file_48f03dab13.webp" alt="МАЦБКТ-СЭЗ" class="lazy-image lazy-image-loaded_false"/></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide"><div class="letterofthanks-card "><button class="absolute overflow-hidden top-20 right-20 w-[1.625rem] h-[1.625rem] z-10"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="letterofthanks-card-link-icon"><path d="M4 16L16 4M16 4V15.52M16 4H4.48" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="letterofthanks-card-link-icon-active"><path d="M4 16L16 4M16 4V15.52M16 4H4.48" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></button><div class="letterofthanks-card-logo-wrapper"><div class="lazy-image-blur letterofthanks-card-logo" style="background-size:contain;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position:center"><img loading="lazy" src="https://minio.nanosemantics.ru/prod-nanosemanticsru-site-media/63f41f4deb58d4c52b87f903f2b31c92_409aed9b15.webp" alt="АтомЭнергоСбыт" class="lazy-image lazy-image-loaded_false"/></div></div><div class="letterofthanks-text-content"><div class="custom-L1 mb-20 text-color9">АтомЭнергоСбыт</div><div class="description custom-L2 text-color7 ">Благодаря появлению на нашем сайте Виртуального помощника Светы, наши клиенты могут оперативно получить ответы на интересующие их вопросы 24/7.</div></div><div class="bg-blur-layer"></div><div class="bg-animated-image-container absolute"><div class="lazy-image-blur bg-animated-image" style="backgroun